snippet.title: Test Tube Titans - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game here: https://ghosttime.itch.io/test-tube-titans

Grow procedurally generated monsters in a lab and then send them out into the world to create havoc using physics-based controls. That's the basic idea behind Test Tube Titans.

Join the discord channel: https://discord.gg/ByhnfzZ
Follow development on twitter: https://twitter.com/TestTubeTitans

Audio by Caleb Winters - https://www.calebwinters.ca/
